high_descs: Turn to your right and walk to the stove, across from you.
Pick up the fry pan on the back, left burner of the stove.
Turn around and walk to the kitchen sink to your left.
Place the fry pan in the sink, turn the water on, rinse out the fry pan, turn the water off, and remove the fry pan from the sink.
Turn around and go to the refrigerator, across from you.
Place the pan, in the refrigerator, on the bottom shelf.
anns.task_desc: Put a clean pan in the refrigerator.

high_descs: Take three steps forward then turn right and walk to the stove so you are facing the left burners.
Pick up the dirty frying pan on the back left burner.
Turn around and take two steps then turn left and walk to the sink.
Wash the pan in the sink and then pick it back up and shut off the water.
Turn around and walk to the fridge.
Put the pan in the fridge then close the fridge door.
anns.task_desc: Put a clean pan in the fridge.

high_descs: go to stove to the right
pick up small round skillet from left, back burner of stove
turn around, go to sink to the left
place skillet in sink, turn on water, turn off water, pick up pan from sink
turn around, go forward to black refrigerator
open refrigerator, place skillet on top right shelf of refrigerator, close refrigerator
anns.task_desc: Place clean skillet on top shelf of refrigerator
